{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_016Ns6GCzDfAKWjnY28Beoo5","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package model\n     2→\n     3→import \"time\"\n     4→\n     5→// Event type constants.\n     6→const (\n     7→\tEventWorkflowStarted   = \"workflow_started\"\n     8→\tEventWorkflowCompleted = \"workflow_completed\"\n     9→\tEventWorkflowFailed    = \"workflow_failed\"\n    10→\tEventWorkflowCancelled = \"workflow_cancelled\"\n    11→\n    12→\tEventActivityScheduled  = \"activity_scheduled\"\n    13→\tEventActivityStarted    = \"activity_started\"\n    14→\tEventActivityCompleted  = \"activity_completed\"\n    15→\tEventActivityFailed     = \"activity_failed\"\n    16→\tEventActivityRetried    = \"activity_retried\"\n    17→\tEventActivityTimedOut   = \"activity_timed_out\"\n    18→\tEventActivityHeartbeat  = \"activity_heartbeat\"\n    19→)\n    20→\n    21→// Event is an immutable log entry tracking state changes (event sourcing).\n    22→type Event struct {\n    23→\tID            int64     `json:\"id\"`\n    24→\tWorkflowRunID string    `json:\"workflow_run_id\"`\n    25→\tActivityRunID string    `json:\"activity_run_id,omitempty\"`\n    26→\tEventType     string    `json:\"event_type\"`\n    27→\tPayload       string    `json:\"payload\"`\n    28→\tCreatedAt     time.Time `json:\"created_at\"`\n    29→}\n    30→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01PjP1ptV6pqXyqjLTjeuXaV","session_id":"f8753322-d9f7-4d57-9d3d-95109e75f16d","uuid":"14590fb2-a0eb-48cd-a955-f26ede928391"}
